OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDJ Greg James leads authors
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fof Dahl spin-off books     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, BBC Radio 1 DJ Greg James is among the 
OL,6, writers who have been commissioned to  
OL,7, create new spin-off stories inspired by
OL,8, Roald Dahl's most famous characters.   
OL,10,FJames and his former newsreader Chris  
OL,11,FSmith have written The Twits Next Door,
OL,12,Fbased on Dahl's 1980 novel The Twits.  
OL,14,FSmith and James said the opportunity to
OL,15,Fwrite a new story based on Dahl's      
OL,16,Fcharacters was "too good to resist".   
OL,18,FThe announcement follows Netflix's     
OL,19,Fpurchase of the rights to Dahl's       
OL,20,Fchildren's books in 2021.              
